 to the emission that occurs when the NS is\ntidally disrupted and accreted by the black hole. The resulting information\nabout the radius of the neutron star may be used to constrain the neutron star\nequation of state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Dec 2007 21:06:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Feb 2008 22:07:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 16 Jul 2008 20:02:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
