ons of Tak\\'acs' theorem are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Dec 2007 00:04:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 May 2008 00:21:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 23 May 2008 05:12:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 5 Sep 2008 23:21:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
